be57c5f6135d97b","tid":1367334,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:33:06.000Z","msg":"!!!一站式 分門別類 公務員 公營機構 開花 Facebook Page!!! 已開：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=8eced605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 分好晒唔同部門，睇睇同事諗緊乜<br />\n2. 集中一個地方，唔同部門間互相打氣，唔使只係自己友圍爐<br />\n3. 綜合唔同平台嘅post, 令力量更大<br />\n4. 不停更新，唔怕post沈底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去呢個Page,可以透過以下方法：<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Form : <a href=\"https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ/exec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscript.google.com%2Fmacros%2Fs%2FAKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ%2Fexec&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=4da661cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ/exec</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook msg: @civilservantsflowers<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=ad24687e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人手勁唔夠，如果有錯有漏麻煩屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\n感激各位冇TLDR<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"8c5f33822b9c7f03991ce0932186ac1016e41873","tid":1367334,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"90cf2e61c88255e801adbbb006df64fc2fdaf5f8","tid":1367334,"uid":41576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f0828a46ba07bc02915ab32f7201497426afb6","tid":1367334,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc76774fea76ca380cc7aeeb287668864024aa","tid":1367334,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"f9a768686f55d303ba2e68138d37432f330193d5","tid":1367334,"uid":19916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}